display_long_description:
Fly through space with style in Soul’s Journey, a multiplayer VR world of freedom, flight, and fun. Catch meteors, discover fun props, and soar with friends across the universe. 

✨ Why play Soul’s Journey?

• Stylish flight – Experience smooth, stylish flying mechanics and feel the freedom of soaring across the universe. 

• Endless possibilities ahead – From unique skins to playful props, new ways to express yourself are always on the horizon. 

• Shape the journey together – Your feedback guides our updates, so you’re not just playing—you’re co-creating the world.

It's a journey we are building together with our community. We release frequent updates and listen closely to player feedback. Join us now in Early Access!

Join our Discord to discover more: https://discord.gg/9jURtuUgHB
